{"tid":2160860,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"邱騰華：會向美方提出經貿交涉 批評共產黨把香港拉入棋盤中 又對美方說武肺才是同共敵人(跪求疫苗)","createTime":"2020-08-17T08:39:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T12:59:00.000Z","uid":21470,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b13fcf6cec527d84258f877909d47f8a6fdebc17","tid":2160860,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:39:42.000Z","msg":"邱騰華：會向美方提出本港產品需標為中國製造問題<br />\n發佈時間 17.08.2020 16:12最後更新時間 17.08.2020 16:12<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局長邱騰華表示，會向美國提出輸美香港產品需貼上「中國製造」標籤的問題，指本港仍正評估有關影響，但強調本港出口商品有限。他形容，香港是被捲入由政治導致的緊張局勢，重申按照世貿組織規定，香港有權標示產品為「香港製造」。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華接受美國財經頻道CNBC訪問時又指，新型冠狀病毒疫情是現時各國在貿易上面對的共同敵人，關注中美緊張關係升級會否令外界分散抗疫的注意力。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2352874\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2352874&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=a767d430\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2352874</a>"},{"pid":"15a888e21ae31c5799dafc787a9254c4624a3062","tid":2160860,"uid":81925,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:41:43.000Z","msg":"You no gun<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d34187c87685c714f3f8058c0e34ede361f993a","tid":2160860,"uid":2656,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:43:10.000Z","msg":"基本法腐乳呢"},{"pid":"c3008ac394d6b1eb4f537c4e354e7382ab303d05","tid":2160860,"uid":177047,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:44:58.000Z","msg":"有著數就愛支，無著數就hk is not china，輸打贏要<br />\n<br />\n你最好搞清楚你愛支定愛錢"},{"pid":"2641b2b7fc612048ed93884e31cbae1e96eed2da","tid":2160860,"uid":61235,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:46:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港有權標示產品為「香港製造」</blockquote><br />\n美國夠有權唔比你入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90d4ec7d7c8995aaddd5e00c4b837135e4faf14c","tid":21